item.dc:creator: @legend-scape legend-scape
item.description:
@legend-scape wrote:

OK, here is a lil tut,

too change the cash and xp of the stall search for stall in client.java until you see,

} if(objectID == 2562){ TheifStall("gem stall", "and recieve 10k", 1, 20*playerLevel[17], 995, 10000, 0x340);

too change the cash of the stall just change the [ 10k + 995, 10000 ] to what eva u wont,
too change the xp rate u can change it too 20 which is quite slow xp,

ok now search for, [ makeGlobalObject(2398, 3484, 2562, 0, 10); ] depends on were ur stall is,

u can now change the [2398, 3484 to were eva u wana put the stall ]

hope i helped ;D,
